<sect2><title>Installation de Diffutils</title><para>Installez Diffutils en lançant les commandes suivantes:</para><para><screen><userinput>LDFLAGS=-static CPPFLAGS=-Dre_max_failures=re_max_failures2 \&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;./configure --prefix=$LFS/static --disable-nls &amp;&amp;make &amp;&amp;make install</userinput></screen></para></sect2>